fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.core

Class DataObjectRefList

  • Object
    • DataObjectPackageElement
      • DataObjectRefList

  • public class DataObjectRefList
extends DataObjectPackageElement
    The Class DataObjectRefList.

    Class for managing list of contained DataObjects either by id or by object reference. Those two modes are useful at different moments of process (import -< ID, DataObjectPackage fusion -< objects...).

    It keeps inner two lists, one of ids and one of DataObjects objects. At a given moment only one list is defined the other one is null. So if you need for example to change DataObjects ID, you have before to force all DataObjectRefList in object reference mode by reading the object references list.
